name: GROUPSHOOT-Sidharth Vemuri
description: Groopshoot is a collaborative application where photographers, regardless of skill, can meet up and go on group photoshoot events. In this application there are a few prototype pages that allow for users to pick the time, location and types of equipment they need. Along with this, they will also have a page that allows them to edit photos and share to a community and receive tips on their photography skills.
